# Frontend Design

- Clean, modern, **minimalistic** UI — prefer whitespace and hierarchy over decoration
- Small reusable widgets; avoid oversized one-off layouts
- Consistent spacing, typography, and color tokens
- No visual clutter: skip unnecessary borders, shadows, pills, badge stacks, and icon rows
- Prefer clear typography and subtle surfaces over heavy card chrome
- Responsive by default (desktop + mobile)
- Match existing design tokens/patterns when extending the app
